{"tid":1712125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以發起一人一信要求停課","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:16:39.000Z","uid":74567,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b4d72afcf90c71d29b003d894ed91c52900f1a","tid":1712125,"uid":74567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"依家咁既勢，教育局一定唔肯停課<br />\n仆街死柒婆講到明 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">停課即係佢地認輸</span><br />\n但大家都知聽日返工對學生而言一定超大影響<br />\n所以 依家係屋企既你 不如召集所有校友 一人一信 要求自己母校停課<br />\n當學生停課 部份家長必需請假返屋企湊仔！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足係到幫你擋子彈 我地係依到都要出盡力</span>"},{"pid":"62c07d39fd5c6708c86edc3a6b9e12affc6417bc","tid":1712125,"uid":127532,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"去學校附近堵路仲實際<br />\n等D家長唔敢叫仔女返學"},{"pid":"2dbf6484fc37aa375ffb1dc0dddf96e8b6317553","tid":1712125,"uid":74567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62c07d39fd5c6708c86edc3a6b9e12affc6417bc","tid":1712125,"uid":127532,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"去學校附近堵路仲實際<br />\n等D家長唔敢叫仔女返學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"太多學校 塞得邊間！"},{"pid":"63a15a3bf3351a8ab6160b85c424c7cce7cb4b51","tid":1712125,"uid":74567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"推 我文筆好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2080f4b2f4e42a424d596db014cfc876ae197d09","tid":1712125,"uid":74567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9d753a894e0b21b26d68a418d78c1aa910b501b","tid":1712125,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:34:49.000Z","msg":"⚠轉出去⚠<br />\n❗大學 Lab 善用化學品反抗❗<br />\n❗HNO3❗<br />\n❗Mg❗<br />\n❗NH4NO3❗<br />\n❗NaOH❗<br />\n❗ANFO❗<br />\n❗ANSU❗<br />\n❗H2SO4❗"},{"pid":"6be71090d9d66939b3b9344a4eeca20436d0e0bd","tid":1712125,"uid":74567,"lik